org.osmdroid.server.jdk

Class TileServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.server.jdk.TileServer

  • public class TileServer
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a simple command list web server (jetty based) that starts up a rest endpoint that serves map tiles. By default it will attempt to start up on port 80.
